## Third-Party Credits

### Image Prompt Guide

The `image-prompt-guide.md` skill is based on materials created by
공냥이 (@specal1849). Original sources:

- Image Prompt 101 Slides: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1rPQVnbu1INJyUAqCvMA7dkO2WzJpD4Q9q_UXq9RH2GU/edit
- PRO Image Prompt Notion: https://fascinated-alley-b43.notion.site/PRO-2b1861d1faaf80b8bf7ef4093827f59b

These materials are used with attribution and transformed into a skill format
for use with AI coding assistants.

### Context Engineering

The `context-engineering-collection.md` skill is based on:

- Agent Skills for Context Engineering by Muratcan Koylan
